00:43:12,300 --> 00:43:15,480
[SPEAKER_00] da smo bile,

624
00:43:15,480 --> 00:43:16,500
[SPEAKER_00] da je to sramota,

625
00:43:16,500 --> 00:43:18,480
[SPEAKER_00] seks i sve vezano za seks,

626
00:43:18,480 --> 00:43:20,840
[SPEAKER_00] za, ajmo reći,

627
00:43:20,840 --> 00:43:21,639
[SPEAKER_00] kratku odjeću,

628
00:43:21,639 --> 00:43:23,519
[SPEAKER_00] previše nas je posramljivalo

629
00:43:23,519 --> 00:43:25,360
[SPEAKER_00] i danas imamo te neke posljedice

630
00:43:25,360 --> 00:43:26,480
[SPEAKER_00] da se svega stidimo.

631
00:43:26,480 --> 00:43:27,840
[SPEAKER_00] Jedna moja prijateljica je meni došla

632
00:43:27,840 --> 00:43:28,199
[SPEAKER_00] i rekla,

633
00:43:28,199 --> 00:43:32,860
[SPEAKER_00] radujem se tom seksu o braku,

634
00:43:32,860 --> 00:43:34,860
[SPEAKER_00] ali isto dobro me jako stid,

635
00:43:34,960 --> 00:43:36,880
[SPEAKER_00] samo si dođen u roditeljima i kaže

636
00:43:36,880 --> 00:43:37,780
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam trudna,

637
00:43:37,780 --> 00:43:39,420
[SPEAKER_00] znači on će znat da sam ja to radila.

638
00:43:39,420 --> 00:43:42,980
[SPEAKER_00] Znači toliko.

639
00:43:42,980 --> 00:43:45,179
[SPEAKER_00] Toliko o tom razmišljamo.

640
00:43:45,179 --> 00:43:46,800
[SPEAKER_00] On će sad razmišljati o tome

641
00:43:46,800 --> 00:43:49,099
[SPEAKER_00] da sam, znači toliko ide taj sram.

642
00:43:49,099 --> 00:43:49,639
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da bi,

643
00:43:49,639 --> 00:43:52,659
[SPEAKER_00] evo rekla da se zapitam

644
00:43:52,659 --> 00:43:55,900
[SPEAKER_00] koliko sam otvorena za nešto

645
00:43:55,900 --> 00:43:57,739
[SPEAKER_00] i ok je da nisam,

646
00:43:57,739 --> 00:44:01,500
[SPEAKER_00] ali da bi jasno iskomunicirala mužu

647
00:44:01,500 --> 00:44:03,239
[SPEAKER_00] što stvarno želim, što ne želim.

648
00:44:03,619 --> 00:44:07,500
[SPEAKER_00] I da naravno da ne moraš raditi ono što ne želiš.

649
00:44:07,500 --> 00:44:09,760
[SPEAKER_00] Sljedeće pitanje, ako smo u vezi,

650
00:44:09,760 --> 00:44:10,920
[SPEAKER_00] to smo prije radili,

651
00:44:10,920 --> 00:44:13,579
[SPEAKER_00] a sad smo se odlučili na čuvanje prije braka,

652
00:44:13,579 --> 00:44:16,860
[SPEAKER_00] vrijedili to isto kao i netko tko nije nikad imao prije odnose

653
00:44:16,860 --> 00:44:18,920
[SPEAKER_00] i trebali se osećati loše kako se riješiti krivnje.

654
00:44:19,039 --> 00:44:21,019
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, definitivno se ne treba osjećati loše.

655
00:44:21,019 --> 00:44:25,360
[SPEAKER_00] Bez ikakve krivnje, jer ako si ispovjedio svoj grijeh

656
00:44:25,360 --> 00:44:26,420
[SPEAKER_00] i krenuo dalje,

657
00:44:26,420 --> 00:44:27,860
[SPEAKER_00] ako je Bog to oprostio,

658
00:44:27,860 --> 00:44:30,420
[SPEAKER_00] onda i ti trebaš raditi na tome da oprostiš sebi

659
00:44:30,420 --> 00:44:33,099
[SPEAKER_00] i da se riješiš oholosti,

660
00:44:33,099 --> 00:44:35,159
[SPEAKER_00] jer to je oholost, ono neopraštanje sebi

661
00:44:35,159 --> 00:44:38,940
[SPEAKER_00] i neimanje povjerenja u Boga.

662
00:44:39,159 --> 00:44:42,079
[SPEAKER_00] Znam da je to jako teško,

663
00:44:42,079 --> 00:44:44,559
[SPEAKER_00] ali definitivno jednako vrijediš

664
00:44:44,559 --> 00:44:48,599
[SPEAKER_00] kao i svi ovi drugi koji su čuvali čistoću.

665
00:44:48,599 --> 00:44:52,940
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, pitanje što stoji za bračnog darivanja

666
00:44:52,940 --> 00:44:53,440
[SPEAKER_00] i što je to,

667
00:44:53,440 --> 00:44:56,980
[SPEAKER_00] ali to smo već odgovorili cijelim ovim predavanjem.

668
00:44:56,980 --> 00:44:58,840
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala nisu si Marija,

669
00:44:58,840 --> 00:45:00,579
[SPEAKER_00] je li grijeh u braku određena poza?

670
00:45:00,579 --> 00:45:01,300
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, nije.

671
00:45:01,300 --> 00:45:02,960
[SPEAKER_00] Sve poze su dozvoljene,

672
00:45:02,960 --> 00:45:05,960
[SPEAKER_00] dok god se muž i žena slažu s tim,

673
00:45:05,960 --> 00:45:07,320
[SPEAKER_00] dok god su otvoreni

674
00:45:07,320 --> 00:45:10,179
[SPEAKER_00] i dok god je njima to ok zajedno

675
00:45:10,179 --> 00:45:11,599
[SPEAKER_00] i mužu i ženju.

676
00:45:11,599 --> 00:45:14,260
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, sve ono što je vama ok,

677
00:45:14,260 --> 00:45:15,360
[SPEAKER_00] go for it.

678
00:45:15,360 --> 00:45:20,139
[SPEAKER_00] Što napraviti ako živimo predbračnom čistoću

679
00:45:20,139 --> 00:45:20,960
[SPEAKER_00] već dvije godine,

680
00:45:20,960 --> 00:45:23,139
[SPEAKER_00] ali nekako ne čekam sushićenja

681
00:45:23,139 --> 00:45:24,059
[SPEAKER_00] na bračnom darivanje,

682
00:45:24,059 --> 00:45:25,239
[SPEAKER_00] nego me to se manje zanima.

683
00:45:25,239 --> 00:45:27,480
[SPEAKER_00] Kao da je nestala želja za tim,

684
00:45:27,480 --> 00:45:28,760
[SPEAKER_00] radi se o zdravoj partnersko vezi

685
00:45:28,760 --> 00:45:29,639
[SPEAKER_00] i zdravom odnosom.

686
00:45:29,639 --> 00:45:31,260
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, prvo bi se zapitala

687
00:45:31,260 --> 00:45:32,659
[SPEAKER_00] zašto ne imam želje s tim,

688
00:45:32,659 --> 00:45:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] kad je ta želja nestala,

689
00:45:34,000 --> 00:45:35,199
[SPEAKER_00] što se to točno dogodilo,

690
00:45:35,300 --> 00:45:37,380
[SPEAKER_00] ali postoje u djetinstvu neke stvari

691
00:45:37,380 --> 00:45:39,840
[SPEAKER_00] zbog koji ih ne imam želju za tim,

692
00:45:39,840 --> 00:45:41,400
[SPEAKER_00] a i definitivno onda razgovarati

693
00:45:41,400 --> 00:45:42,500
[SPEAKER_00] o odnosu s partnerom,

694
00:45:42,500 --> 00:45:43,239
[SPEAKER_00] iskreno reći,

695
00:45:43,239 --> 00:45:43,900
[SPEAKER_00] gledaj, ono,

696
00:45:43,900 --> 00:45:47,159
[SPEAKER_00] to i to se događa kod mene,

697
00:45:47,159 --> 00:45:48,360
[SPEAKER_00] kako je to kod tebe.

698
00:45:48,360 --> 00:45:50,380
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, iskreno porazgovarati

699
00:45:50,380 --> 00:45:53,559
[SPEAKER_00] i možda čak se posavjetovati

700
00:45:53,559 --> 00:45:54,380
[SPEAKER_00] s nekim stručnim,

701
00:45:54,380 --> 00:45:55,780
[SPEAKER_00] bio to neki svećenik

702
00:45:55,780 --> 00:45:58,360
[SPEAKER_00] ili bračni terapeut.

703
00:45:58,360 --> 00:46:00,119
[SPEAKER_00] U ovom slučaju

704
00:46:00,119 --> 00:46:02,699
[SPEAKER_00] nije došlo do braka,

705
00:46:02,699 --> 00:46:03,960
[SPEAKER_00] ali evo, prije braka obaviti

706
00:46:03,960 --> 00:46:05,099
[SPEAKER_00] definitivno dobar razgovar

707
00:46:05,099 --> 00:46:06,599
[SPEAKER_00] da se vidi koja je pozadina

708
00:46:06,599 --> 00:46:08,980
[SPEAKER_00] toga da ne želiš

709
00:46:08,980 --> 00:46:11,099
[SPEAKER_00] bračno darivanje.

710
00:46:13,579 --> 00:46:15,159
[SPEAKER_00] Mogu li postojati problemi

711
00:46:15,159 --> 00:46:16,440
[SPEAKER_00] u braku između muža i žene

712
00:46:16,440 --> 00:46:17,199
[SPEAKER_00] u slučaju da žena

713
00:46:17,199 --> 00:46:18,440
[SPEAKER_00] zarađuje više od muškarce

714
00:46:18,440 --> 00:46:19,260
[SPEAKER_00] i može li utjecati

715
00:46:19,260 --> 00:46:21,400
[SPEAKER_00] to na muškarčeva autoritet u braku?

716
00:46:21,400 --> 00:46:25,679
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerujem da ako postoje

717
00:46:25,679 --> 00:46:26,840
[SPEAKER_00] ovi problemi,

718
00:46:26,840 --> 00:46:28,719
[SPEAKER_00] što se tiče da to utječe

719
00:46:28,719 --> 00:46:30,059
[SPEAKER_00] na muškarčeva autoritet,

720
00:46:30,059 --> 00:46:32,579
[SPEAKER_00] da se prvo on treba zapitati

721
00:46:32,579 --> 00:46:34,360
[SPEAKER_00] zašto je njemu to bitno

722
00:46:34,360 --> 00:46:35,500
[SPEAKER_00] da on zarađuje više,

723
00:46:35,500 --> 00:46:38,840
[SPEAKER_00] što to zarađivanje govori

724
00:46:38,840 --> 00:46:39,840
[SPEAKER_00] o njemu kao osobi.

725
00:46:39,840 --> 00:46:41,380
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, vjerojatno da imam

726
00:46:41,380 --> 00:46:42,739
[SPEAKER_00] problem s tim da

727
00:46:42,739 --> 00:46:46,239
[SPEAKER_00] to uvjerenje,

728
00:46:46,239 --> 00:46:47,340
[SPEAKER_00] ono, zarađujem više,

729
00:46:47,340 --> 00:46:48,260
[SPEAKER_00] vrijedim više.

730
00:46:48,260 --> 00:46:50,960
[SPEAKER_00] Pa onda, čim žena zarađuje više,

731
00:46:50,960 --> 00:46:53,019
[SPEAKER_00] automatski se osjeća bezvrijednim.

732
00:46:53,019 --> 00:46:56,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ali mislim da se to jednim razgovorom

733
00:46:56,420 --> 00:46:58,440
[SPEAKER_00] i s tim što za njeg znači

734
00:46:58,440 --> 00:46:59,159
[SPEAKER_00] zarađivati više,

735
00:46:59,159 --> 00:47:00,099
[SPEAKER_00] što njemu predstavlja

736
00:47:00,099 --> 00:47:01,280
[SPEAKER_00] da žena zarađuje više,

737
00:47:01,280 --> 00:47:02,460
[SPEAKER_00] a da on zarađuje manje,

738
00:47:02,460 --> 00:47:04,039
[SPEAKER_00] što njemu ga to dovodi

739
00:47:04,039 --> 00:47:04,659
[SPEAKER_00] u konflikt.

740
00:47:04,659 --> 00:47:06,460
[SPEAKER_00] Definitivno razgovor

741
00:47:06,460 --> 00:47:06,880
[SPEAKER_00] i naravno,

742
00:47:06,880 --> 00:47:08,139
[SPEAKER_00] ako je neka ozbiljna situacija

743
00:47:08,139 --> 00:47:09,179
[SPEAKER_00] stvarno preporučila

744
00:47:09,179 --> 00:47:11,460
[SPEAKER_00] bračnu psihoterapiju.

745
00:47:11,900 --> 00:47:14,920
[SPEAKER_00] voljela bih čuti

746
00:47:14,920 --> 00:47:16,199
[SPEAKER_00] neku realnu priču

747
00:47:16,199 --> 00:47:17,059
[SPEAKER_00] u borbu sa održavanjem

748
00:47:17,059 --> 00:47:17,920
[SPEAKER_00] bračne čistoće.

749
00:47:17,920 --> 00:47:19,239
[SPEAKER_00] Bližen se braku,

750
00:47:19,239 --> 00:47:20,400
[SPEAKER_00] znam što vjera podrazumije

751
00:47:20,400 --> 00:47:21,360
[SPEAKER_00] pod bračnom čistoćom,

752
00:47:21,360 --> 00:47:22,500
[SPEAKER_00] ono sve je to super i divno,

753
00:47:22,500 --> 00:47:23,239
[SPEAKER_00] međutim,

754
00:47:23,239 --> 00:47:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da je teško

755
00:47:24,000 --> 00:47:24,880
[SPEAKER_00] živjeti baš kao i

756
00:47:24,880 --> 00:47:25,860
[SPEAKER_00] predbračnu čistoću.

757
00:47:25,860 --> 00:47:26,340
[SPEAKER_00] Evo nadam,

758
00:47:26,340 --> 00:47:27,480
[SPEAKER_00] znači ovo predavanje

759
00:47:27,480 --> 00:47:31,519
[SPEAKER_00] i ovo što sam sad pričala,

760
00:47:31,519 --> 00:47:32,440
[SPEAKER_00] bar malo pomoć,

761
00:47:32,480 --> 00:47:33,300
[SPEAKER_00] ako ne onda

762
00:47:33,300 --> 00:47:35,400
[SPEAKER_00] sa slobodom možete javiti

763
00:47:35,400 --> 00:47:37,219
[SPEAKER_00] za neka dublja pitanja.

764
00:47:37,219 --> 00:47:41,219
[SPEAKER_00] Najviše muči

765
00:47:41,219 --> 00:47:42,900
[SPEAKER_00] što nemam volje za sponost,

766
00:47:42,900 --> 00:47:44,079
[SPEAKER_00] posebno sad kad sam trudna,

767
00:47:44,079 --> 00:47:44,860
[SPEAKER_00] također mi se zanima

768
00:47:44,860 --> 00:47:46,079
[SPEAKER_00] koje su poze prihvatljive.

769
00:47:46,079 --> 00:47:47,460
[SPEAKER_00] To smo pričali o,

770
00:47:47,460 --> 00:47:50,139
[SPEAKER_00] znači neke žene kad su trudne,

771
00:47:50,139 --> 00:47:51,280
[SPEAKER_00] ono imaju baš

772
00:47:51,280 --> 00:47:53,559
[SPEAKER_00] jak libido,

773
00:47:53,559 --> 00:47:54,860
[SPEAKER_00] ne žele sve,

774
00:47:54,860 --> 00:47:56,360
[SPEAKER_00] sve žele probati otvornost za sve,

775
00:47:56,360 --> 00:47:57,599
[SPEAKER_00] neke jednostavno nemaju

776
00:47:57,599 --> 00:47:59,420
[SPEAKER_00] i to stvarno treba iskomunicirati mužem

777
00:47:59,420 --> 00:48:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] i vidjeti način

778
00:48:02,000 --> 00:48:03,840
[SPEAKER_00] na koji možemo postić

779
00:48:03,840 --> 00:48:05,980
[SPEAKER_00] da se taj libido podigne,

780
00:48:05,980 --> 00:48:09,300
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno kako same sebi pomoći,

781
00:48:09,300 --> 00:48:10,519
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno kako mužu reći

782
00:48:10,519 --> 00:48:11,500
[SPEAKER_00] da nam pomogne,

783
00:48:11,500 --> 00:48:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] jer smo oboje uključeni u to

784
00:48:13,000 --> 00:48:14,380
[SPEAKER_00] i naravno sve su

785
00:48:14,380 --> 00:48:16,219
[SPEAKER_00] poze prihvatljive.

786
00:48:17,460 --> 00:48:20,639
[SPEAKER_00] Da li se žena mora darovati mužu

787
00:48:20,639 --> 00:48:21,780
[SPEAKER_00] kad joj se ne da

788
00:48:21,780 --> 00:48:22,639
[SPEAKER_00] i nije raspoložena

789
00:48:22,639 --> 00:48:24,800
[SPEAKER_00] ako on pokaže želju za istim.

790
00:48:24,800 --> 00:48:26,960
[SPEAKER_00] Znači u ovom slučaju bih rekla

791
00:48:26,960 --> 00:48:28,420
[SPEAKER_00] da se dogovarate,

792
00:48:28,420 --> 00:48:30,699
[SPEAKER_00] planirate to bračno darivanje,

793
00:48:30,699 --> 00:48:33,079
[SPEAKER_00] posebno ako tu još ima i djece

794
00:48:33,079 --> 00:48:36,420
[SPEAKER_00] i ako je taj život u kaosu,

795
00:48:36,420 --> 00:48:37,659
[SPEAKER_00] da se dogovarate

796
00:48:37,659 --> 00:48:38,780
[SPEAKER_00] ti pa tad i tad

797
00:48:38,780 --> 00:48:40,860
[SPEAKER_00] da se može te pripremiti.

798
00:48:40,860 --> 00:48:43,360
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerujem da kad nama žena

799
00:48:43,360 --> 00:48:43,920
[SPEAKER_00] moja kaže

800
00:48:43,920 --> 00:48:45,219
[SPEAKER_00] evo aj sad, pa sad ono,

801
00:48:45,219 --> 00:48:46,719
[SPEAKER_00] pa kako sad,

802
00:48:46,780 --> 00:48:47,679
[SPEAKER_00] ne mogu sad ono,

803
00:48:47,679 --> 00:48:49,099
[SPEAKER_00] sad sam u spremanju,

804
00:48:49,099 --> 00:48:50,199
[SPEAKER_00] ne mogu ostaviti robu

805
00:48:50,199 --> 00:48:50,920
[SPEAKER_00] i ne ispeglanu,

806
00:48:50,920 --> 00:48:52,619
[SPEAKER_00] ali kad se mi pripremimo

807
00:48:52,619 --> 00:48:54,239
[SPEAKER_00] cijeli dan

808
00:48:54,239 --> 00:48:55,300
[SPEAKER_00] kad onako znamo to

809
00:48:55,300 --> 00:48:56,119
[SPEAKER_00] nas najveći čeka

810
00:48:56,119 --> 00:48:57,699
[SPEAKER_00] i shvatimo to kao jednu nagradu,

811
00:48:57,699 --> 00:48:58,559
[SPEAKER_00] ono bit će mi baš super,

812
00:48:58,559 --> 00:48:59,659
[SPEAKER_00] jedva čekam, jedva čekam

813
00:48:59,659 --> 00:49:01,039
[SPEAKER_00] da bi se to ovaj,

814
00:49:01,039 --> 00:49:02,179
[SPEAKER_00] drugačije bi se

815
00:49:02,179 --> 00:49:04,179
[SPEAKER_00] ta želja razvijala

816
00:49:04,179 --> 00:49:05,239
[SPEAKER_00] i baš bi ono,

817
00:49:05,239 --> 00:49:06,960
[SPEAKER_00] to bila kao jedna nagrada

818
00:49:06,960 --> 00:49:07,719
[SPEAKER_00] na kraju dana.

819
00:49:07,900 --> 00:49:08,300
[SPEAKER_00] tako da evo,

820
00:49:08,300 --> 00:49:09,219
[SPEAKER_00] ja bi definitivno

821
00:49:09,219 --> 00:49:10,320
[SPEAKER_00] pokušala

822
00:49:10,320 --> 00:49:12,360
[SPEAKER_00] s tim vidjeti

823
00:49:12,360 --> 00:49:13,219
[SPEAKER_00] što mi točno,

824
00:49:13,219 --> 00:49:14,840
[SPEAKER_00] zašto to ne želim,

825
00:49:14,840 --> 00:49:16,179
[SPEAKER_00] je li mi nešto ne odgovara

826
00:49:16,179 --> 00:49:17,360
[SPEAKER_00] ili

827
00:49:17,360 --> 00:49:18,980
[SPEAKER_00] možda pokušati s tim

828
00:49:18,980 --> 00:49:19,960
[SPEAKER_00] da se planira

829
00:49:19,960 --> 00:49:21,119
